The Seafarer’s Tax Calculator is the easiest and fastest way to calculate your SED (Seafarer’s Earnings Deduction). We’ve come up with the most efficient and hassle-free tax calculator.   <br>
The website and App draws upon HMRC’s rules to determine and explain if you’re entitled to a tax return and how much. If you need a clear and uncomplicated guide to Seafarers Earnings Deduction, then look no further! 
