		</div></div></div><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-2-1" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-2-1-0" ><div class="panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-2-1-0-0"><h3 class="widget-title">Criteria for SED</h3>			<div class="textwidget">• Working on a ship<br>
• Must be employed (not self employed)<br>
• Be UK resident<br>
• Initially complete a qualifying period of 365 days<br>
• At least 183 days must be outside of the UK<br>
• Visit at least one foreign port per employment<br>
• Cumulative days in the UK should not be greater than the days out of the UK</div>
